  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to implement and evaluate a lifestyle program designed
      to help women who have high glucose levels during pregnancy make healthful diet and physical
      activity changes to lose weight. Eligible women will be randomly assigned to life-style
      intervention or usual medical care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
